    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Official ceremonial visits to a place by a dignitary, noble, pope, head of state, or other person of authority, often accompanied by a retinue in procession and ceremony, including a formal greeting by dignitaries of the visited location.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
